entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have completed the podracer's tasks.
entries.journal_entry_description: Finishing this race will prove to An'Kwee that you have racers blood. If you fail the race you may speak to Draknus or the race droid to restart the race.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: This is the final race. It will require speed and quick decisions. Race the course in the required time. Check in with the race timer to start the race.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Check In with the Race Timer to Start Race
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Proceed to waypoint 1 before the timer runs out.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Proceed to waypoint 2 before the timer runs out.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Proceed to waypoint 3 before the timer runs out.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Proceed to waypoint 4 before the timer runs out.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Proceed to waypoint 5 before the timer runs out.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Talk to the race timer to check your time.
